payload.text: Brainstorm reasonable ideas regarding how does a dead lobster find its way into a suburban yard inland from an ocean?

metadata.objective: This is a true story and I am looking for logical explanations. A lobster was found in a 2 acre lawn at least 15 miles from the ocean. There are no resturants in the vicinity nor abnormal human or animal presence. The lobster was likely alive within the past 24 hours of being found on the lawn. Its body was fully intact. FHow did this happen?
